  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b5efdff692f883768f7f32728bb7cc1b.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1170 height=354 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When tyranny takes control… someone has to pull the trigger. <strong>Machine Gun Fury</strong> is a bold revival of the classic arcade military shooter — no cover systems, no moral debates, just pure reflex-driven carnage. It’s you, your trigger finger, and a limited supply of grenades against entire armies. If you grew up blasting through classic arcade games, welcome back to the frontline, soldier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/53c4c1600c5a0424b2ae6faa280e2daa.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/53c4c1600c5a0424b2ae6faa280e2daa.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/53c4c1600c5a0424b2ae6faa280e2daa.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast your way through enemy armies with nothing but sharp reflexes, heavy firepower, and a limited supply of grenades. Liberate 8 explosive regions packed with screen-filling bosses, relentless waves of enemies, and high-intensity run-and-gun action.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/eab426f467a81a0cde5ead28c0fb8346.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/eab426f467a81a0cde5ead28c0fb8346.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/eab426f467a81a0cde5ead28c0fb8346.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the boots of three unstoppable soldiers armed to the teeth and ready to bring tyranny to its knees:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gunner Jimbo</strong> – A walking assault division. Built for suppressive fire and zero compromise. If he stops shooting, something big is about to explode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Suzi Uzi</strong> – Fast, tactical, and merciless. She doesn’t waste bullets. She doesn’t miss. She doesn’t stop moving.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mini-Gun Floyd</strong> – The embodiment of sustained fire. When those barrels spin up, the battlefield becomes a memory.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three warriors. One impossible mission. Infinite enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b2e97820b2b1e3cdbfc06b3f76717053.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b2e97820b2b1e3cdbfc06b3f76717053.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b2e97820b2b1e3cdbfc06b3f76717053.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight on foot or take control of heavily armed vehicles including tanks, boats, and combat buggies. Unleash a full arsenal of military-grade weaponry and trigger explosive chain reactions that turn enemy strongholds into rubble. If it moves — eliminate it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/3af42ee2494610f6505c93edf1de3980.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/3af42ee2494610f6505c93edf1de3980.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/3af42ee2494610f6505c93edf1de3980.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced <strong>top-down and side-scrolling run-and-gun gameplay</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full range of combat weaponry delivering large-scale destruction and huge body counts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Authentic 8-bit pixel art powered by modern enhancements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destructible elements, screen shake, particle effects, and layered parallax backgrounds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explosive SID-inspired soundtrack that hits like an arcade cabinet turned up to max</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press Start. Pull the trigger. Feel the Fury.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b5efdff692f883768f7f32728bb7cc1b.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1170 height=354 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When tyranny takes control… someone has to pull the trigger. <strong>Machine Gun Fury</strong> is a bold revival of the classic arcade military shooter — no cover systems, no moral debates, just pure reflex-driven carnage. It’s you, your trigger finger, and a limited supply of grenades against entire armies. If you grew up blasting through classic arcade games, welcome back to the frontline, soldier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/53c4c1600c5a0424b2ae6faa280e2daa.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/53c4c1600c5a0424b2ae6faa280e2daa.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/53c4c1600c5a0424b2ae6faa280e2daa.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast your way through enemy armies with nothing but sharp reflexes, heavy firepower, and a limited supply of grenades. Liberate 8 explosive regions packed with screen-filling bosses, relentless waves of enemies, and high-intensity run-and-gun action.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/eab426f467a81a0cde5ead28c0fb8346.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/eab426f467a81a0cde5ead28c0fb8346.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/eab426f467a81a0cde5ead28c0fb8346.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the boots of three unstoppable soldiers armed to the teeth and ready to bring tyranny to its knees:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gunner Jimbo</strong> – A walking assault division. Built for suppressive fire and zero compromise. If he stops shooting, something big is about to explode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Suzi Uzi</strong> – Fast, tactical, and merciless. She doesn’t waste bullets. She doesn’t miss. She doesn’t stop moving.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mini-Gun Floyd</strong> – The embodiment of sustained fire. When those barrels spin up, the battlefield becomes a memory.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three warriors. One impossible mission. Infinite enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b2e97820b2b1e3cdbfc06b3f76717053.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b2e97820b2b1e3cdbfc06b3f76717053.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b2e97820b2b1e3cdbfc06b3f76717053.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight on foot or take control of heavily armed vehicles including tanks, boats, and combat buggies. Unleash a full arsenal of military-grade weaponry and trigger explosive chain reactions that turn enemy strongholds into rubble. If it moves — eliminate it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/3af42ee2494610f6505c93edf1de3980.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/3af42ee2494610f6505c93edf1de3980.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/3af42ee2494610f6505c93edf1de3980.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced <strong>top-down and side-scrolling run-and-gun gameplay</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full range of combat weaponry delivering large-scale destruction and huge body counts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Authentic 8-bit pixel art powered by modern enhancements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destructible elements, screen shake, particle effects, and layered parallax backgrounds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explosive SID-inspired soundtrack that hits like an arcade cabinet turned up to max</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press Start. Pull the trigger. Feel the Fury.</p>",
